    "Support for Kafka, S3, and GCS connections",
    "Materialized views, copy pipes, and sink pipes",
    "JWT token creation for secure scoped access",
    "Local development mode with Docker",
    "Branch-based development workflow",
    "Migration tool for existing Tinybird projects"
